Package: lancedb
Title: R Client for LanceDB Embedded Vector Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("LanceDB Contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dev@lancedb.com")
Description: Provides an R interface to LanceDB, an embedded vector database for
    AI applications. Uses Rust bindings via 'extendr' for high performance.
    Supports lazy query building with 'dplyr'-compatible verbs (filter, select,
    slice_head, arrange, collect) for both vector similarity search and table
    scans. Queries are built lazily and executed only when collected, following
    the same pattern as 'dbplyr'.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/lancedb/lancedb
BugReports: https://github.com/lancedb/lancedb/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc (>= 1.70)
Imports:
    rlang (>= 1.0.0),
    dplyr (>= 1.1.0),
    arrow (>= 12.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
